</ul>

<h2>How to Use Eardogger</h2>

<ol>
  <li>Sign up for a free account.</li>
  <li>Install the "Mark my spot" and "Where was I" bookmarklets on all your devices and browsers. (See below.)</li>
  <li>To pause whatever you're reading, click "Mark my spot."
    <ul>
      <li>If you've dogeared that site before, that's it! The dogear now marks your new position.</li>
      <li>If this is a new site, Eardogger asks you for the site's name and makes a new dogear. (You can also adjust the URL prefix, for sites that share a domain with several other sites.)</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>To resume reading a site from where you paused it, use the list of dogears on the <a href="/">Eardogger homepage</a>.
    <ul>
      <li>Or, if you're already on that site, click "Where was I." (Good for when you left a tab open but then read further on another device.)</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ol>

